social_posts.post_text: This last year has had its mountain tops and it’s extremely low valley’s. I’ve went through a lot of personal battles that I’ve chosen to keep private for obvious reasons and I’ve also dealt with alot of loss that I didn’t think I could make it through, then God brought this beautiful Lady into my life and she has showed me a Kind of Love I didn’t even know existed. I just want to say thank you for loving me the way you do and for all the silly/goofy moments that I wouldn’t trade for nothing. I’m better because of you!!
I’m so honored to be apart of this event and I can’t wait to be out there y’all!! Make sure and grab y’all’s tickets.
